 紅毛火船歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%87-Ng%E1%BA%A1c/Kh%C3%AA-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-S%C3%A0o-tuy%E1%BB%81n-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-t%C3%A1c/poem-WhF4Gg_5CDUVSM0RdGJNIQ">Khê Thượng Sào tuyền thượng tác - 溪上巢泉上作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%87-Ng%E1%BA%A1c/author-sa85iEQrSGk1mnTgBoNSDQ">Lệ Ngạc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/S%C6%A1n-T%C3%A2y-th%C3%A0nh-y%E1%BA%BFt-Ch%C3%A2u-Phong-c%C3%B4ng-th%E1%BB%8B-d%E1%BA%A1-d%E1%BB%AF-Minh-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-t%C3%BAc/poem-PZ_jYkPHa6NU1Ndta4EyOQ">Sơn Tây thành yết Châu Phong công, thị dạ dữ Minh Trọng túc - 山西城謁珠峰公是夜與明仲宿</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0-Nh%C6%B0/Xu%C3%A2n-tr%E1%BA%A3n/poem-TwPNKykTc5jPc4mfW7JdGQ">Xuân trản - 春盞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0-Nh%C6%B0/author-mhAlF-W1JHQDMsH_S0aV3Q">Hà Như</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
